Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:38.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\frz270\pos(1265,360)}四散的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:45.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\frz270\pos(1265,360)}記憶的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:54.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\frz270\pos(1265,360)}獨自一人渴求著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.51,0:23:00.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\frz270\pos(1265,360)}沒有指望的解救
